txt.en: 'I cannot understand how so many goblins can exist here, unless they have some great hoard of supplies stowed away in Gazatmur.\n\n'If you encounter any food-stores, please do feel free to destroy them utterly. We ought to discourage the goblins from lengthening their stay in the Great Delving.'
'Well done, [placeholder]! That was a key step in dismantling their presence here. Now they will have to look elsewhere for food.'
'Gazatmur is just yonder, and I am almost positive there is a great amount of food amassed within.'
The food-stores of the goblins can be found in Gazatmur and provide the goblins with extended sustenance.
Goblin food-stores can likely be found in Gazatmur in the eastern Great Delving.\n\nYou should destroy food-stores in Gazatmur to dismantle this camp as an established keep for the enemy.
Wigfast is perched just beyond Gazatmur in the Great Delving.\n\nYou should return to Wigfast.
